This following tools are required to run this application on the server which executes it.

1. Install pip via the command: sudo apt-get install pip
2. Install virtualenv via the command: pip install virtualenv
2. Create a virtualenv via: virtualenv name_of_your_virtualenv
3. Install Openssh-client and openssh-server via the command: sudo apt-get install openssh-client && sudo apt-get install openssh-server
4. Install p7zip via the command : sudo apt-get install p7zip-full p7zip-rar
6. Install paramiko via the command : pip install paramiko
7. Add the following command in the crontab file: * /1 * * * python cron.py
8. Install MongoDB util on cron's server: mongodump thru command line
9. Install MySQL util on application server: pip install mysql-connector-python
10. Install MySQL Client on cron's server: sudo apt-get install mysql-client


